title: HOUR 2- Jordan Palmer Aug 25, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 2- Jordan Palmer Aug 25, 2020
description:
Jordan Palmer tells Dan that he always wants to know how a player will play when he is not favored to win. Jordan says he wants to see how confident a player is and how mature they show they can be in big moments.
